summary:
Kena Reveals What Makes Its AI-Powered Music Creator Economy Different - With the recent push of Kena's crypto utility token on the Avalanche blockchain, Kena is maturing into a decentralized economy powered by AI. Kena helps artists retain all their earnings and additionally redistributes10% of the collective earnings of the network to all artists.

 Kena develops Artificial Intelligence that can learn from any music within seconds and teach millions globally. - With the recent release, Kena claims a 96% accuracy in giving nuanced, human-like feedback to music practitioners just by listening to them practice!
